cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new neural model for machine translation. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with capturing contextual information from a document, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it proposes a new neural model for machine translation.
